AWS Aythentication Setup - 

2 ways - access keys and iam roles

Access keys way ->
We go to IAM -> Create a IAM user with admin policy
We create secret credentials, we get access and secret keys
On system -> install aws cli
apt-get install aws-cli

aws configure
enter the keys

IAM Role way ->
Create a IAM role-> admin policy  and attach this role to the EC2 machine